#: ../../source/how_to/compare_two_scenarios.rst:85
msgid ""
"**Mismatched dimensions.** If you ran the two scenarios with different "
"``hour`` or ``month`` settings, ``ds_a - ds_b`` will fail with a "
"broadcast error. Keep configs in lockstep when comparing."
msgstr ""

#: ../../source/how_to/compare_two_scenarios.rst:89
msgid ""
"**NPV-discounted vs nominal.** ``ds.cost`` is NPV; ``ds.gen`` is in MWh "
"per timestep. Don't mix without dividing by ``var_factor[year, zone]`` "
"for unit conversion."
msgstr ""

#: ../../source/how_to/compare_two_scenarios.rst:92
msgid ""
"**One-hot scenarios.** For more than two variants, lift the pattern into "
"a dict comprehension over a list of suffixes: ``{s: "
"xr.open_dataset(f\"output/baseline_{s}.nc\") for s in suffixes}``."
msgstr ""

